license             GPL-2
maintainers         umich.edu:egull

description         A package for the calculation of spectral functions using the Maximum Entropy method
long_description    This package provides functionality for computing the analytical continuation \
                    of many-body response functions from the imaginary time axis to the real frequency \
                    axis. This code is part of the ALPS applications and dependent on the ALPSCore \
                    libraries.

